snippet.title: Rescue - Everyday Heroes - Trailer US-Version[FULL HD]
snippet.description:
The US Version on "Rescue - Everyday Heroes" will be released on the 11the december 2013 on STEAM!


A complete new enviroment, new original US-vehicles and a new freeplay map wait for you! Explore the new scenario and be a US-firefighter and coordinate your control station.

The US Version of "Rescue" will be releaed firstable just in english language. Other language versions will follow ion the next weeks and the game will automatically update if you start the STEAM Version.
